<bibRefCitation author="Dendy" box="[1236,1388,1292,1317]" firstAuthor="Dendy" pageId="18" pageNumber="19" pagination="1 - 164" refId="ref43241" refString="Dendy, A. (1922) Report on the Sigmatotetraxonida collected by H. M. S. ' Sealark' in the Indian Ocean. In: Reports of the Percy Sladen Trust Expedition to the Indian Ocean in 1905. Fol. 7. Transactions of the Linnean Society of London, Series 2, 18 (1), pp. 1 - 164, pls. 1 - 18." type="journal article" year="1922">Dendy 1922</bibRefCitation>
