<paragraph blockId="20.[199,811,151,320]" box="[199,702,260,285]" pageId="20" pageNumber="21">• C-shaped with spines on the outer curve.</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="20.[199,811,151,320]" box="[199,641,295,320]" pageId="20" pageNumber="21">• Subdermal cavities filled with sand</paragraph>
